These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, watermelon, pepper, cranberry, peas
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, jazz, gospel, dubstep, techno
1. the fan of dubstep is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating blueberry is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of gospel##2
6. the person eating peas is in the middle##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of techno##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | watermelon | blueberry | peas | cranberry | pepper |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | techno      | dubstep   | hip-hop     | jazz    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, juice
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, sailing, juice-polo, handball
1. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is juice-polo##1
3. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is juice-polo##2
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate       | juice    | coffee | mirinda   |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | cricket | juice-polo | handball      | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, photography, chess, dancing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, jazz, indie, ambient, classical
1. the fan of ambient is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
5. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
6. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | photography | collecting | chess    | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | techno        | indie      | jazz | classical      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, drawing, reading, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, animation, zombie, horror, comedy
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
2. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | traveling      | reading | drawing | filmmaking   | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | comedy    | zombie        | action | animation |

