.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, fanta, juice
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, polish, french, mexican, italian
1. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the italian##1
4. the french is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the italian is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the mexican##1
7. the polish is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | juice      | hot-chocolate | cola   | fanta  | almond-milk  |
| Nationality   | french | mexican | colombian | polish | italian |

