.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, soy-milk, water, coffee
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, pilot, doctor, freelancer, coffeecher
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
2. the pilot is between the coffeecher and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the pilot##1
5. the doctor is the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the doctor is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
8. the freelancer is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | fanta        | hot-chocolate                | water  | soy-milk  | coffee            |
| Job        | accountant | coffeecher | pilot | doctor | freelancer |

