.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, coffee, juice, fanta
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, software-developer, mechanic, teacher, chef
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
