4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
7. the videographer is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the chef is on the right of the software-developer##1
9. the teacher is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage   | fanta       | coffee   | tea    | juice    | iced-tea |
| Job        | mechanic | videographer | software-developer | chef | teacher     |

