3. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching drama movies##2
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
