.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, spanish, italian, pakistani, french
5 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, snake, frog, lizard
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the pakistani is the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the frog is the pakistani##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the spanish is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the italian is between the spanish and the colombian##2
7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the italian##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | french | spanish | italian     | colombian | pakistani |
| Pet           | cat | ferret     | snake | lizard    | frog      |

