3. the person who's sport is surfing is the scientist##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is in an odd position##4
6. the software-developer is on the left of the dressmaker##1
7. the designer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | software-developer | dressmaker | designer | scientist | manager |
| Sport   | golf | skiing | handball    | surfing    | basketball  |

