.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There 5 different types of food: kale, peach, grapefruit, lettuce, pineapple
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, cycling, skiing, biathlon
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the person eating kale is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is soccer##2
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating grapefruit##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | peach    | pineapple  | kale      | lettuce     | grapefruit |
| Sport   | swimming | soccer | skiing | cycling | biathlon |

