.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, nectarine, blueberry, apricot, zucchini
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, train, airplane, scooter, subway
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the subway is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
5. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the subway and the person eating nectarine##2
7. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Food        | apricot | zucchini | asparagus  | blueberry | nectarine     |
| Transport   | train  | airplane     | subway | taxi      | scooter |

