.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, hot-chocolate, water, juice
There are 5 different nationalities: german, japanese, dutch, turkish, american
1. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the turkish is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking 7up is between the german and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the japanese##3
8. the german is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up | water   | sprite   |
| Nationality   | turkish | japanese | american  | german | dutch |

