.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
There 5 different types of food: radish, broccoli, orange, banana, mango
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, camping, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person eating broccoli##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | mango   | banana  | broccoli     | radish | orange |
| Hobby   | puzzles | sudoku | drawing | camping | rock-climbing      |

