5. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
7. the japanese is in an odd position##4
8. the german is in the middle##1
9. the nigerian is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
