.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, punk, country, funk, folk
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, roller, helicopter, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the fan of funk is the person driving the roller##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is between the fan of punk and the person driving the ship##2
5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | funk | country     | folk     | punk |
| Transport     | quad-bike   | roller   | ship | helicopter | skateboard  |

