.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, family, time-travel, adventure
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, tram, ship, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
9. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | comedy | adventure     | family | time-travel |
| Transport     | ship       | airplane   | tram | scooter   | motorbike        |

