.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, gardening, fishing, hiking
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, french, turkish, colombian, indonesian
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the turkish is the turkish##1
3. the colombian is on the far left##1
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the indonesian##2
6. the french is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the indonesian##2
7. the colombian is in an odd position##4
8. the indonesian is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | fishing | gardening | skydiving | hiking | video-games     |
| Nationality   | colombian    | french   | indonesian       | turkish | egyptian |

