.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, funk, classical, pop, r&b
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, van, motorbike, car, subway
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the car##2
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
5. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the subway is the fan of d&b##1
7. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | classical      | pop | r&b     | funk      |
| Transport     | subway | van | car | boat | motorbike |

 